1	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2	-- Title      : AxiStream BatcherV1 Protocol: https://confluence.slac.stanford.edu/x/th1SDg
3	-- Title      : AxiStream BatcherV2 Protocol: https://confluence.slac.stanford.edu/x/L2VlK
4	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5	-- Company    : SLAC National Accelerator Laboratory
6	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7	-- Description: The firmware batcher combines sub-frames into a larger super-frame
8	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
9	-- This file is part of 'SLAC Firmware Standard Library'.
10	-- It is subject to the license terms in the LICENSE.txt file found in the
11	-- top-level directory of this distribution and at:
12	--    https://confluence.slac.stanford.edu/display/ppareg/LICENSE.html.
13	-- No part of 'SLAC Firmware Standard Library', including this file,
