-- Title      : Line Code 8B10B: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/8b/10b_encoding
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Company    : SLAC National Accelerator Laboratory
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Description: 8B10B Encoder Module
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
